definitions.definition: to propose, to suggest, to offer (to suggest a plan or course of action)

parsedExamples.example: 그리고 세번째로 우리 여성 의류의 영역에 있어서 향상을 제안하고 싶습니다.
parsedExamples.transliteration: Geurigo sebeonjjae-ro uri yeoseong uiryu-ui yeong'yeog-e isseoseo hyangsang-eul jean-hago sipseumnida.
parsedExamples.translation: and thirdly, I’d like to suggest some improvements in our range of womenswear.
